The development team (hereinafter referred to as "Developers" or "Company") declares that its fundamental goal is the design, development, and implementation of an innovative digital product. All activities of the Company are aimed at creating a sustainable technological infrastructure and ecosystem intended to provide Users with cutting-edge tools for growth, interaction, and the potential to benefit from using the platform.

The Developers commit to making all necessary commercial and technical efforts (best efforts) to:

• Ensure stable operation and continuous improvement of the product;
• Develop functionality and expand the platform's integration capabilities;
• Promote the project in the international market and scale its ecosystem.

The Company confirms its commitment to the long-term development of the project in the interests of the entire user community.
